      "detail": "Widely available GPU infrastructure means the processor faces no hardware barrier to running additional derivation cycles. Each recursive training round uses the same commodity hardware. The low infrastructure barrier means recursive derivation is limited only by economics, not by hardware scarcity. Merchant GPU availability enables any well-funded processor to pursue recursive value extraction."
    },
    "Supply Control": {
