      "memo": "Standard alignment through RLHF generates preference data from human feedback that itself becomes a valuable derived dataset feeding back into recursive training.",
      "detail": "RLHF alignment produces human preference data as a byproduct. This preference data is itself a valuable training input for the next model generation. The alignment process creates exhaust data that enters the recursive value chain. RLHF is both an alignment technique and a data-generation mechanism. The preference data generated during alignment is one of the highest-value recursive inputs."
    },
    "Security Posture": {
